{"tid":1140854,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陶傑：快支持林鄭「迎難而上」，加快通過修訂「引渡法」，千萬不要退縮呀。","createTime":"2019-05-06T06:00:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-06T16:50:10.000Z","uid":34156,"like":615,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"8cdb389c8f359106e19bde911554705d3712b713","tid":1140854,"uid":34156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T06:00:07.000Z","msg":"美中貿易談判，川普露出底牌：與其放虎歸山，不如一棍打殘。<br />\n<br />\n香港股市，半日大跌千點。<br />\n<br />\n美國已經嚴正警告林鄭：若敢頑固堅持修訂所謂罪犯引渡法，置香港美加歐洲僑民於險境，外國企業會開始撤出香港。<br />\n<br />\n「好打得」的林鄭，相信一定不會被帝國主義八國聯軍的欺凌壓倒，否則她就會遭到中國人民的鄙視和歷史的唾棄了。<br />\n<br />\n快支持林鄭「迎難而上」，加快通過修訂「引渡法」。林鄭，千萬不要退縮呀。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Oyuom2t.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOyuom2t.png&h=716ee549&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/272574169481780/posts/2649076278498212?s=100001997040105&amp;v=i&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F272574169481780%2Fposts%2F2649076278498212%3Fs%3D100001997040105%26v%3Di%26sfns%3Dmo&d=JxdAuiyzJYRXF2tJvMOkN0ngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=b77f921a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/272574169481780/posts/2649076278498212?s=100001997040105&amp;v=i&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"522da94ff71212e4326d7d66e0a9b47401afb2da","tid":1140854,"uid":34156,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T06:01:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f4275affec425f868957808b3e13c69adf94cb5","tid":1140854,"uid":34156,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T06:03:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ee1438aeba7bb96a1b2aeef2d6b2c78391cf440","tid":1140854,"uid":9564,"like":12,"dislike":48,"score":-36,"citedBy